{"type": "article", "id": 6374, "title": "兔子跨栏大赛", "description": null, "date": "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": null, "author": 8, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 1, "image": "img/default_images/missing_article.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一场来自英国约克郡的兔子跨栏比赛现场。于是，来自世界各地的兔子和主人们都来踊跃参赛了。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t在兔子跨栏界，大长腿不是关键，体重看起来问题也不是特别大，就是弹跳力很重要。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'sans serif', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;\">“她在跳的时候真的很享受。看看她就知道，她有多开心了。”一个主人说道。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<iframe height=\"498\" width=\"640\" src=\"http://player.youku.com/embed/XNTI5MTE2OTk2\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\">\r\n</iframe>\n\n\n"}